20/01/2006
MADRID, Spain -- Serbia-Montenegro Foreign Minister Vuk Draskovic discussed the situation in Kosovo and the upcoming status negotiations with Spain's King Juan Carlos I on Thursday (19 January). Afterwards, Draskovic said that he asked the king to help seek a compromise, in which the legitimate interests of majority Albanians and minority Serbs would be met. (Tanjug, RTS - 19/01/06) 
